
Realizar a limpeza das pastas abaixo:

cd /VMDS/backup/
rm -rI sw-data_new/

cd /backup/
rm -rI sw-data_new/

cd /VMDS/ds_transfer/ds_electric
rm -rI *

Realizar parada dos Serviços:

Parar servidores de banco no NetXMS - Colocar em manutenção
Parar Pods(JS, GSS e STS) - Via Headlamp
SWMFS: 

sh /opt/swmfs_stop.sh
ps -ef | grep swmfs
find /VMDS/ -name *.jou

Realizar cópia da base para pasta /VMDS/backup local nos 4 Serviodres:

cd /VMDS/backup/
cp -rpv /VMDS/sw-data_new/ /VMDS/backup/

Subi o serviço SWMFS:

sh /opt/swmfs_start.sh
ps -ef | grep swmfs

Validar cópia da base para o disco local /VMDS/backup:

find /VMDS/backup/sw-data_new -type f -name "*.sfi" -exec sed -i 's|/VMDS/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_electric|/VMDS/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_electric|g' {} +
find /VMDS/backup/sw-data_new -type f -name "*.sfi" -exec sed -i 's|/VMDS/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db|/VMDS/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db|g' {} +
find /VMDS/backup/sw-data_new -type f -name "*.sfi" -exec sed -i 's|/VMDS/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_conductors|/VMDS/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_conductors|g' {} +
find /VMDS/backup/sw-data_new -type f -name "*.sfi" -exec sed -i 's|/VMDS/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_structural|/VMDS/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_structural|g' {} +


Realizar cópia da base disco /backup:

cd /backup/
tmux
rsync -aHAX --numeric-ids --progress /VMDS/backup/ /backup/

Alterar aquivos .sfi para validar a copia da base no disco /backup:

find /backup/sw-data_new -type f -name "*.sfi" -exec sed -i 's|/VMDS/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_electric|/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_electric|g' {} +
find /backup/sw-data_new -type f -name "*.sfi" -exec sed -i 's|/VMDS/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db|/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db|g' {} +
find /backup/sw-data_new -type f -name "*.sfi" -exec sed -i 's|/VMDS/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_conductors|/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_conductors|g' {} +
find /backup/sw-data_new -type f -name "*.sfi" -exec sed -i 's|/VMDS/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_structural|/backup/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_structural|g' {} +

Finalizar as sessões tmux abertas:

tmux kill-server

Realizar a limpeza da pasta abaixo:

cd /VMDS/backup/
rm -rI sw-data_new/

Realizar cópia da base para pasta /VMDS/backup local nos 4 Serviodres:

cd /VMDS/backup/
cp -rpv /VMDS/sw-data_new/ /VMDS/backup/

Caso necessário conceda as permissões abaixo no script:

chmod x start_eo53_split.sh
chmod 777 start_eo53_split.sh


Remover arquivos gdb do destino:

find /VMDS/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_electric -name "*gdb*" -print
find /VMDS/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_electric -name "*gdb*" -exec rm -rf {} +

Acessar o diretorio onde estão os arquivos gdb que serão copiados:

find /VMDS/ds_transfer/ds_electric -name "*gdb*" -print
cd /VMDS/ds_transfer/ds_electric
\cp -rpv *gdb* /VMDS/sw-data_new/sw_prd_db/ds_electric/



